                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-06-09</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">读书没什么用，不会让你腰缠万贯不会让你平步青云；读书又很有用，至少让你成为一个更好的自己。每个读书人都值得尊敬，不管他入世还是脱俗，至少他肯静下心来去读书去作书，这就足够伟大。先做个称职的读者，先当个用心的听众</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="440768913">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-440768913" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-440768913" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="440768913">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/doudoumai/">白墨</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2011-09-28</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">有几篇访谈挺有启发，詹宏志的，长平的等</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

